 <html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
       xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
       xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal">
    <div>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>Your profile ${api.settings['site_name']} has been changed.</p>
        <p tal:condition="first_name">
        The first name on your account is now ${first_name}.
        </p>
        <p tal:condition="last_name">
        The last name on your account is now ${last_name}.
        </p>
        <p>If you wish to review your ${api.settings['site_name']} information and view a list of other foundation resources go to <a href="${request.route_url('home')}">${api.settings['site_name']}</a>.</p>
        <p>Please do not reply to this message. Replies to this message are routed to an unmonitored mailbox. If you have questions please <a href="${request.route_url('contact_us')}">contact us</a>.</p>
        <p>Thank you,</p>
        <p>${api.settings['site_name']}</p>
    </div>
 </html>
